{
  "stem": "3804.5",
  "chunk_idx": 4,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 4.7,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "And then I made him exercises.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "I put on him the dress-- dress, you know.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "And suddenly in one of the evenings, I got-- I knew, because we didn't know what we're going to do with him.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "There's going to be an airplane from El Al that will being him to Israel.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "And that was a new thing.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "We didn't know.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "And that was-- that was-- that happened because it was 150 years of the independence, and we caught him at that time.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "It was accident.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "And Abba Eban came, the head of the team, to celebrate, you know, the independence, to have a good relationship with-- with Argentina.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "And suddenly, when we kept him, we say-- and he didn't know what we were going to bring, was never told the purpose of coming of this airplane.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "And then the whole thing was to bring him to the airplane.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "And Eichmann-- and we-- and when we brought him there, he was very angry that he was left behind.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "The airplane left with Eichmann, leaving him behind.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "That was very-- I think that Israel and-- and how do you call him?-- Abba Eban have been very angry at each other, because he made him as a bait, you know, for-- for bringing the airplane.",
      "word_count": 37
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Did Abba Eban-- Abba Eban did not know?",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Did not know-- no.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And that was a terrible thing.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And then we broke relationship.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And there was a big thing about six-- I don't know-- about one year, had a lot of problems between the two countries, because they said we have done something against the law.",
      "word_count": 33
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "We kidnapped somebody as a-- their resident.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "The-- how do you say?",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And we have to bring him back.",
      "word_count": 7
    }
  ],
